title: Epson Expression Premium XP-830 | Take the Tour of the Small-in-One Printer
description:
This wireless Small-in-One printer offers superior photo quality. It features a 30-page Auto Document Feed, auto 2-sided printing, copying, scanning and faxing, and borderless photos up to 8" x 10".

For more information, visit: http://bit.ly/2nHfDx5
